g.text: Workflow that iterates all numeric columns and negates the values in the column.
The loop takes one column at a time, renames the column name to
ANONYMOUS_COLUMN in the first rename node, changes the value in the math
formula nodes and reverts the name to the original column name.
The columns are collected in the loop end node and finally joined with the
unmodified part of the original input table.
